What do you enjoy most on the weekends
Having been through a busy week, I would like spend some time to retreat into myself on the weekend. I mean I just want to ignore what's happening around me and give all of my attention to my hobbies. I usually visit a coffee shop near my house and enjoy a cup of coffee while reading a book or listening to my favorite playlist. Sometimes, I hang out with my closed friends for a catch-up. When we get together, we usually play games, catch a flick, or go for a scroll to unwind, recharge our batteries, and being fully-prepared for the next week.

